  "state_prompts": [
    "## State: START\n- **Description:** Navigate to All West page\n- **Triggers:**\n\t1. If it is on the chrome homescreen\n- **Actions:**\n\t1. Go to https://shop.allwest.com/order/1 word for word\n\t2. TERMINATE AT THIS POINT",
